; Whisper Shrine — Assassin intro arena.
; Hidden temple-courtyard built into a cliff cleft. Black-stone floor with
; faint glyph etchings. Pools of dark water along the edges. Five hooded
; statues circle the central platform, each holding a different blade.
; Master Sapum waits in the dark of the back arch.

